sim.util

Class Queue

  • java.lang.Object
    • sim.util.Queue

  • public class Queue
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple Queue of Objects, implemented in an array. (I tried generics, but java complains about arrays of generics, thank you very much). It's not synchonized, so don't expose it to multiple threads!
    See Also:
    but improved to hold k elements in an array of length k, not k-1.
